FBIS4-9572 "dreeu082_r_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-082 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 ROMANIA Spokesman Cited on Possible Visit by Ex-King Spokesman Cited on Possible Visit by Ex-King AU2604162094 Bucharest Radio Romania Network in Romanian 1300 GMT 26 Apr 94 AU2604162094 Bucharest Radio Romania Network Romanian BFN [Text] Responding to a question from one of our correspondents on King Mihai's intention to visit Romania during the Easter holidays, the spokesman for the Ministry of Foreign Affairs stated that a decision will be made soon if the contacts currently taking place confirm the private nature of that visit, including the king's relations with Romanian authorities, reports our correspondent Doina Saiciuc.
